<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>نا عَبْدُ الرَّزَّاقِ<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>١٣٦٢ - عَنْ مَعْمَرٍ , عَنْ قَتَادَةَ ,<span class="c5"> فِي قَوْلِهِ تَعَالَى:</span> <span class="c3">{شَدِيدُ الْمِحَالِ}</span> <span class="c4">[الرعد: ١٣]</span> ,<span class="c5"> قَالَ:</span> <span class="c1">" إِذَا مَحَلَ , يَعْنِي الْهِلَاكَ ,<span class="c5"> يَقُولُ:</span> فَهُوَ شَدِيدٌ "</span> ,<span class="c5"> قَالَ مَعْمَرٌ:</span> وَقَالَ قَتَادَةُ: <span class="c2">«شَدِيدُ الْحِيلَةِ»</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>